(1518, '_transient_customizr-pro-update-response', 'O:8:\"stdClass\":13:{s:11:\"new_version\";s:5:\"2.1.7\";s:14:\"stable_version\";s:5:\"2.1.7\";s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Customizr Pro\";s:4:\"slug\";s:13:\"customizr-pro\";s:3:\"url\";s:62:\"http://presscustomizr.com/extension/customizr-pro/?changelog=1\";s:12:\"last_updated\";s:19:\"2018-08-02 13:49:02\";s:8:\"homepage\";s:50:\"http://presscustomizr.com/extension/customizr-pro/\";s:7:\"package\";s:202:\"http://presscustomizr.com/edd-sl/package_download/MTUzNTIxNzkyOTozZmRiY2ViMTJlNDlkZDY3MjcxMjdjYjRjNGZhMDY1Njo0MDI4MjpjN2M4MTA1MTEyY2FlNmUzYWE0MzNhNGUwOTE0YmVhNDpodHRwc0AvL3dvcmRwcmVzcy5tdGhhaXplLmZyOjA=\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:202:\"http://presscustomizr.com/edd-sl/package_download/MTUzNTIxNzkyOTozZmRiY2ViMTJlNDlkZDY3MjcxMjdjYjRjNGZhMDY1Njo0MDI4MjpjN2M4MTA1MTEyY2FlNmUzYWE0MzNhNGUwOTE0YmVhNDpodHRwc0AvL3dvcmRwcmVzcy5tdGhhaXplLmZyOjA=\";s:8:\"sections\";a:2:{s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:77941:\"<p><strong>= 2.1.7 August 1st 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>added : new option to display the site title next to the logo. Enabled by default.</li>\n<li>imp : always make sure WC functions exist before calling them.</li>\n<li>imp : replace slider iphone checks with checkboxes consistent with the Gutenberg editor style.</li>\n<li>imp : better compatibility with the Gutenberg editor for post-formats metaboxes.</li>\n<li>imp: update masonry quote post format CSS according to the new core code</li>\n<li>fix: wrong post order on masonry grid layout (RTL)</li>\n<li>fix: do not stretch the featured pages image to 100% of the height if not requested</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.6 June 19th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: do not wrap ol item counters.</li>\n<li>Fix: improve scoping of the link underline effect only to widgets we know</li>\n<li>Fix: do not print related posts by tags when the post has no tags.</li>\n<li>Impr: improve some woocommerce checkout elements alignment.</li>\n<li>Impr: when reacting to the post-load event make sure the response object is defined.</li>\n<li>Impr: dropdown on hover: make sure pointer events on scroll are still allowed if there\'s at least one submenu opened</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.5 June 6th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: radio and checkboxes style that should be applied only to relevant elements to avoid plugin conflits ( contact forms plugins for example ).</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.4 June 1st 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: GDPR compliance comment-form-cookies-consent label and input appearance.</li>\n<li>Fix: search form close icon visual issue in IE10+.</li>\n<li>Fix: no need to enqueue the front placeholders assets when user not logged in.</li>\n<li>Fix: make sure the mfp gallery left arrow is correctly aligned.</li>\n<li>Fix: set word-wrap break-word for whatever text in the page content. This will avoid text overflowing the parent element width, for example in list items</li>\n<li>Imp: make sure .navbar-brand height is set to auto to avoid issues with bootstrap3 based plugins.</li>\n<li>Imp: build/delete retina version of pdf thumbnails. Also improve remove retina images logic.</li>\n<li>Imp: do not load dev classes</li>\n<li>Imp: decrease space above WooCommerce page title.</li>\n<li>Added: options to fine tuning singular featured image height in smartphones<br />\nboth in modern and classical style</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.3 March 29th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: author meta link pointing to wrong URL.</li>\n<li>Fix: Use of deprecated class constructor not supported since PHP7</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.2 March 26th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : the topbar contact infos could be printed on desktop devices, even when set to be displayed only on mobiles</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.1 March 23rd 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: wrong text-domain for the social links module</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.1.0 March 22nd 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: do not display post metas for pages in search results</li>\n<li>Fix: make sure our col*auto always have a max-width of 100%.</li>\n<li>Imp: overall css improvements</li>\n<li>Imp: remove post \'hentry\' class when current post type is a page since author and published/update metas will not be printed in pages. In blog/archives or single posts showing those metas is up to the user.</li>\n<li>Imp: co-authors plus plugin integration</li>\n<li>Imp: add horizontal widget area before the footer.</li>\n<li>Imp: add early check on php version (min 5.3) and wp version (min 4.5)</li>\n<li>Imp: turn slider .czrs-title from H1 to H2</li>\n<li>Imp: fix various form plugins compatibility</li>\n<li>Imp: improve woocommerce single product tabs style</li>\n<li>Imp: added various dismissable placeholders and notices on front with direct link to the live customizer.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.26 February 13th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: tagline visibility in mobiles when shown in desktop topbar.</li>\n<li>Fix: topbar menu not displayed in fresh installs.</li>\n<li>Fix: move hardcoded contact-info CSS rule into theme stylesheed.</li>\n<li>Fix: fix RTL article\'s hierarchical tax separator.</li>\n<li>Fix: fix checkbox/radio compatibility with WPForms by reverting the webkit appearance override.</li>\n<li>Imp: allow pointer events on scroll if submenu opened(hover) CSS</li>\n<li>Imp: avoid possible issues with very old PHP versions in menu customizer</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.25 February 1st 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Imp: slightly decrease the font-size of the contact info block</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.24 January 31st 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: display the 404 content only when we\'re really in the 404 context</li>\n<li>Fix: make author bio RTL compliant</li>\n<li>Fix: RTL breadcrumb separator displayed with wrong direction.</li>\n<li>Fix: RTL submenu default opening direction</li>\n<li>Imp: Woocommerce - allow lightbox effect and smartload in product short description</li>\n<li>Imp: RTL submenu compliance 1) submenu animations 2) caret rotation adjustment when is RTL</li>\n<li>Imp: Woocommerce - better u/o list styling for the product short description</li>\n<li>Imp: remove body itemprop itemtype structured data. Fix issues with missing microformats reported by the google-search-console in static pages</li>\n<li>Added: new options to display contact informations : opening hours, phone and email in the topbar</li>\n<li>Added: a new option to choose on which devices ( desktops, mobiles, both ) the topbar should be displayed</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.23 January 16th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: tagline not displayed in the header</li>\n<li>Fix: wording typo in the featured pages description placeholder</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.22 January 16th 2018 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: vertical menu items with children and expand on click not styled when using the Font Customizer</li>\n<li>Fix: the number of feat. pages by line option disappearing after selection in the customizer</li>\n<li>Fix: animated underline not removable in some navigation menus. Also do not underline current menu item when the underline hover effect option is disabled</li>\n<li>Fix: WP icon font-family possible override with the pro Font Customizer</li>\n<li>Fix: list in wc product description missing list style type</li>\n<li>Fix: slider caption not centered in ipad Mini</li>\n<li>Fix: clicking menu items with children and no URL bring to 404</li>\n<li>Fix: remove unwanted vertical separator before comments link in single posts</li>\n<li>Improved: improve mobile menu horizontal alignment</li>\n<li>Improved: full page search form focus/blur on overlay open/close</li>\n<li>Improved: upgraded the Font Awesome icon set to its latest version</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.21 December 27th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : possible \"headers already sent\" error in WordPress admin</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.20 December 24th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : WooCommerce Terms and Condition checkbox in Checkout page is not really visible</li>\n<li>Fix : dropdown menu-item word-break property set to break-word. Fixes</li>\n<li>Improved : Font Customizer, better UI and improved performances</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.19 December 20th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: decrease regular submenu top to 15px.</li>\n<li>Fix: avoid adding slider metabox to attachment which are not images</li>\n<li>Fix: widget categories title transformed to uppercase. apply the uppercase rule only to its list items also remove the bold font-weight</li>\n<li>Fix: always display the comment form before comment list (if any)</li>\n<li>Fix: slider cta hiding text</li>\n<li>Fix: related posts height after the content with two sidebar</li>\n<li>Fix: fix search icon not appearing in the topbar</li>\n<li>added: a boxed layout options for the header, the content and the footer</li>\n<li>added: new option to allow a menu dropdown on click for mobile menu and side menu. Enabled by default on mobile devices</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.18 November 20th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : WP 4.9 Code Editor issue could impact the custom css customizer option when checking errors in the code</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.17 November 15th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: post/page layout meta box must show the contextualized default layout</li>\n<li>Fix: fix header/overlay search label not custom skinned</li>\n<li>Fix: fix potential slider captions overlapping on page load</li>\n<li>Imp : more precis title of the topbar menu</li>\n<li>Imp: add new options to control the singular blocks location. author box (single post), related posts (single post), comments ( single posts and pages )</li>\n<li>Imp: add mobile header search location option</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.16 November 6th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : label padding for comment text area applied to other inputs</li>\n<li>Fix : input white background applied to unwanted selectors</li>\n<li>Fix : mCustomScrollbar =&gt; the scrollers are positionned at the bottom on the first instantiation</li>\n<li>Fix : fix grid items opacity 0 not applied on init when infinite scroll is enabled</li>\n<li>Fix : fix better check on whether Customizr is using or not concatenated scripts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.15 November 5th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : WooCommerce, make wc-cart header button act like a dropdown only when displaying the wc-cart widget (so not when displayed in the mobile header). fixes #1274</li>\n<li>Added : Doc search in the theme admin page \"About Customizr\"</li>\n<li>Imp : style of the comment text area</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.14 October 29th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : update notification showing again despite clicking on dismiss</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.13 October 27th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : fix some woocommerce form layout issues. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link tooltipped tooltipped-ne\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1243\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"267533700\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" aria-label=\"#1243, [Customizr] WooCommerce - Account Details Password change input broken layout.\">#1243</a></li>\n<li>Fix : WP 4.9 compatibility =&gt; in WP v4.9, the control options are not wrapped in the params property but passed directly instead</li>\n<li>Fix : image description in attachment not correctly displayed. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1231\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"266560242\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1231\">#1231</a></li>\n<li>Fix : single attachment date meta should not be a link. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1233\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"266587169\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1233\">#1233</a></li>\n<li>Fix : added missing retina (x2) placeholder images</li>\n<li>Fix : don’t collapse mobile mene when scrolling fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1226\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"266271898\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1226\">#1226</a></li>\n<li>Fix : slider caption text size still too big on mobile. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1235\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"266796151\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1235\">#1235</a></li>\n<li>Fix : update the way we get woocommerce cart url according to the new api + backward compatibility. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1223\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"265582593\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1223\">#1223</a></li>\n<li>Fix : fix possible wrong responsive images URL for sliders in multisite installs. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1247\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"268109632\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1247\">#1247</a></li>\n<li>Fix : remove the active callback of the front page content section in the customizer. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1252\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"268402182\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1252\">#1252</a></li>\n<li>Fix : WP4.9 compat customizer additional CSS default. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1255\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"268720095\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1255\">#1255</a></li>\n<li>Fix : hover style on comment date links. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1114\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"245966703\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1114\">#1114</a></li>\n<li>Fix : if comments are displayed by the user ( option is checked ) always show comment history, even if comment are closed. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1253\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"268570838\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1253\">#1253</a></li>\n<li>Fix : removed no results and 404 quotations, probably wrongly attributed to authors. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1142\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"251614727\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1142\">#1142</a></li>\n<li>Fix : make sure the 404 content is always displayed when is_404() even if have_posts() is true. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1260\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"269096584\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1260\">#1260</a></li>\n<li>Imp : better the way to store when the user started using the theme</li>\n<li>Imp : performance improvement by implementing lazyloading for the main slider. Images are loaded when the become visible. New specific option in advanced &gt; performance</li>\n<li>Imp : always close the mobile menu expanded when resizing</li>\n<li>Imp : increased the .comment_link font-size in related posts</li>\n<li>Imp : an anchor ‘linear’ scroll effect can be set by adding the attribute data-anchor-link=”true” to a link</li>\n<li>Imp : add custom page template for the modern style. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1209\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"263826693\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1209\">#1209</a></li>\n<li>Imp : footer credits translation strings and link title.</li>\n<li>Imp : footer colophon is now text-align:center for smartphones in portrait mode &lt;=&gt; media-breakpoint-down(xs)</li>\n<li>Imp : bulleted and numbered lists formatting. Second line should be indented to the start of the text of the first line. added more space before and around. fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1102\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"245633851\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1102\">#1102</a> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1183\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"260004120\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1183\">#1183</a> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1224\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"265830934\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1224\">#1224</a> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1228\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"266388612\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1228\">#1228</a></li>\n<li>Imp : wraps the_content() in the div.czr-wp-the-content element in the templates printing the wp content : singulars ( including attachment ) and plain post grid</li>\n<li>Imp : add specific model and templates to render the post attachment of type image content</li>\n<li>Imp : slider nav dots made smaller for mobiles @media-breakpoint-down(xs)</li>\n<li>Imp : better styling for post metas. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1113\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"245958864\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1113\">#1113</a></li>\n<li>Added : a layout field meta box option for attachments. =&gt; if the layout is not set for a particular attachment, it will be inherited from the parent ( which is the current behaviour )</li>\n<li>Added : the anchor scroll for the comment link in single posts</li>\n<li>Added : new option to control the visibility of the slider navigation bullets. Implement <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1207\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"263805818\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1207\">#1207</a></li>\n<li>Added : [pro] head and footer script editor in the customizer &gt; advanced panel &gt; additional scripts. Can be used to add Google Analytics code or any custom scripts or stylesheets</li>\n<li>Added : [pro] Add gallery carousels for gallery post formats in lists of posts : masonry and alternate thumbnails type.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.12 October 12th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : Infinite scroll Uncaught TypeError: Cannot read property \'element\' of undefined at Scroller.maybeLoadMejs</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>= 2.0.11 October 9th 2017 =</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix : global skin CSS not printed when no custom header skin. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1215\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"263858165\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1215\">#1215</a>.</li>\n<li>Fix : various html fixes like duplicated ids or data attributes</li>\n<li>Fix : featured pages not translated by wpml. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1205\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"263432495\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1205\">#1205</a></li>\n<li>Fix : don\'t update the defaults when wp_installing()</li>\n<li>Fix : preview error on singulars. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1194\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"261366640\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1194\">#1194</a></li>\n<li>Fix : typo in customizer controls</li>\n<li>Fix : slider caption elements, default Fittext minsizes too high. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1191\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"261049707\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1191\">#1191</a></li>\n<li>Fix : link whole slide not including the caption. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1140\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"251611641\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1140\">#1140</a></li>\n<li>Fix : colors of the search form in dark overlay. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1185\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"260214542\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1185\">#1185</a></li>\n<li>Fix : closing slide\'s title h1 html tag. Fixes <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" href=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1188\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"260580726\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/presscustomizr/customizr/issues/1188\">#1188</a></li>\n